        <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;The application &lt;code&gt;pinentry&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; opens when you need to provide your password for
decrypting your GnuPG key. You can install different interfaces for providing
the password via &lt;code&gt;pinentry&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;. There are graphical and non-graphical variants
e.g.,&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre style=&quot;background-color:#2b303b;color:#c0c5ce;&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ dpkg -l | grep pinentry
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;pinentry-curses
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;pinentry-gnome3
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;pinentry-gtk2
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;pinentry-tty
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
</summary>
        
